VALIDATION_SCHEMA:
{
  "definitions": {},
  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
  "$id": "http://example.com/root.json",
  "type": "object",
  "title": "The Root Schema",
  "required": [
    "employeeNumber",
    "tripNumber",
    "tripType",
    "travelMode",
    "departureDate",
    "arrivalDate",
    "origin",
    "destination",
    "createdBy",
    "tripPurpose",
    "tripStatus",
    "approvalRemarks"
  ],
  "properties": {
    "employeeNumber": {
      "$id": "#/properties/employeeNumber",
      "type": "string",
      "title": "The Employeenumber Schema",
      "default": "",
      "examples": [
        "00029359"
      ],
      "minLength": 1,
      "pattern": "^(.*)$"
    },
    "tripNumber": {
      "$id": "#/properties/tripNumber",
      "type": "string",
      "title": "The Tripnumber Schema",
      "default": "",
      "examples": [
        "4464546"
      ],
      "minLength": 1,
      "pattern": "^(.*)$"
    },
    "tripType": {
      "$id": "#/properties/tripType",
      "type": "string",
      "title": "The Triptype Schema",
      "default": "",
      "examples": [
        "I"
      ],
      "minLength": 1,
      "pattern": "^(.*)$"
    },
    "travelMode": {
      "$id": "#/properties/travelMode",
      "type": "string",
      "title": "The Travelmode Schema",
      "default": "",
      "examples": [
        "Air"
      ],
      "minLength": 1,
      "pattern": "^(.*)$"
    },
    "departureDate": {
      "$id": "#/properties/departureDate",
      "type": "string",
      "title": "The Departuredate Schema",
      "default": "",
      "examples": [
        "2019-02-12"
      ],
      "format": "date",
      "pattern": "^(.*)$"
    },
    "arrivalDate": {
      "$id": "#/properties/arrivalDate",
      "type": "string",
      "title": "The Arrivaldate Schema",
      "default": "",
      "examples": [
        "2019-02-12"
      ],
      "format": "date",
      "pattern": "^(.*)$"
    },
    "origin": {
      "$id": "#/properties/origin",
      "type": "string",
      "title": "The Origin Schema",
      "default": "",
      "examples": [
        "Chennai"
      ],
      "minLength": 3,
      "pattern": "^(.*)$"
    },
    "destination": {
      "$id": "#/properties/destination",
      "type": "string",
      "title": "The Destination Schema",
      "default": "",
      "examples": [
        "Delhi"
      ],
      "minLength": 3,
      "pattern": "^(.*)$"
    },
    "createdBy": {
      "$id": "#/properties/createdBy",
      "type": "string",
      "title": "The Createdby Schema",
      "default": "",
      "examples": [
        "00029359"
      ],
      "minLength": 1,
      "pattern": "^(.*)$"
    },
    "tripPurpose": {
      "$id": "#/properties/tripPurpose",
      "type": "string",
      "title": "The Trippurpose Schema",
      "default": "",
      "examples": [
        "business"
      ],
      "minLength": 1,
      "pattern": "^(.*)$"
    },
    "tripStatus": {
      "$id": "#/properties/tripStatus",
      "type": "string",
      "title": "The Tripstatus Schema",
      "default": "",
      "examples": [
        "A"
      ],
      "minLength": 1,
      "pattern": "^(.*)$"
    },
    "approvalRemarks": {
      "$id": "#/properties/approvalRemarks",
      "type": "string",
      "title": "The Approvalremarks Schema",
      "default": "",
      "examples": [
        "Approved. all ok."
      ],
      "minLength": 1,
      "pattern": "^(.*)$"
    }
  }
}
